{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz nehutte tas Kalps def-\nmits Kameetus / no fawa Kunga\nKameeteem/ un atsgahje/ un wiſ-\nfada Manta fawa Kunga / bij\nwizza Rohká/ un wiſsch zehlehs/\nun gabje uhs Mesopotamiju/unhs\nRaôra Pilsfahtu."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad likke wiſsch tohß Ka-\nmeetus apnestees ahra / preeſſch\nta Pilsfahta/pee weenas Uhdens-\nAkkas/ap Wakkara Laiku/tai Lai-\nká/kad tahs Sinehlejas ahra nah-\nze/ un wiſsch fazzija:"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "KUNGS / tu DEews\nmanna Kunga Abbrâaima / fa-\nstohpi man fhodeen / un darri\nSchehlastibu pee manna Kunga\nAbbrâaima."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Reds/ es stahwu pee tahs\nUhdens Akkas/ un fcha Pilsfahta\nLauschu Meitas ees ahra / Uhd-\nni finelt."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad lui noteek/ ka ta jan-\nna Meita/ us ko es fazzischu / pa-\ngahs jelle tawn Traunku / ka es\ndsert warru / un ta fazzihs/ dserr/\nestawus Kameetus arridsan dsir-\ndinaschu/ ta patti (effoti)/ ko tu\ntawam Kalpan Jhsâakam no-\nwehlejis / un ka es pee ta atsiht\nwarru/ ka tu Apschehlofchanu pa-\nrahdtiis effi mannam Kungam."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notikke/ pirms tas\nbij pabeidsis runnaht/ rangi/tad\nnahze Rebekka ahra/ kas bij dsim-\nnuti Betuetam / Milkas tahs\nNaôra Seetwas / Abbrâaima\nBrahta Dehlam/ un tai bij wiſ-\nnas Traunks wirs faweem Ka-\nwiescheem."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tai Micitinaí bij feht\nſkaists Waigs/ta bij weena Tum-\npratva/ un ne weens Wihrs bij te\natsinnis/ ta nokahpe Akká/ un pil-\ndija fawu Traunku / un uskahpe\natkát."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad tezzeja tas Kalps wiſ-\nnai pretti / un fazzija : lai es jelle\nkahdu Uhdens Malzinu no taw-\nTrauka nodserrohs."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta fazzija : Dserr/mane\nKungs/ un ta steidsahs/ un nolaide\nto Traunku us fawu Rohku / un\ndsirdija winnu."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad ta bij pabeiguf-\nwinnu dsirdinaht / fazzija ta : es\nfinelfchu arridsan preeſſch taweem\nKameeteem."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta steidsahs / un iſlehje\nfawu Trauku dsirdijamâ Sille/\nun tezzeja atkat us Akku finelt: un\nfinehle wiſſeem winna Kameeteem"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Wihrs isfabrihni-\njahs pahr tahs/ kluiffu zeesdauns/\nka wiſsch fajustu / arrig tas\nKUNGS / winna Zettam lizzis\nlabbi isdohtees / jeb ue."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad tee Kameeti bij no-\ndsehrufschees/tad nehme tasWihrs\nweenu selta Peeres-Sprahdst / ta\nfivehre weenu puſsSihkeli/un di-\nwt apleekamus Rohku - Gredse-\nuns / pee winnas Rohkahin/ tee\nfwehre Definitis Sihketus."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſsch fazzija : Mei-\ntina / kurras Meita tu effi ? pa-\nfakki man jelle to / Irrag preeſſch\nnuus tawa Tehwa Namma-\nWeetas/ tur Nafts-Mahju dab-\nbuht?"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
